### Retrieve a user by id

GET {{host}}/user/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### Retrieve a user by username

GET {{host}}/user?username=Stefania
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### Save a new user

POST {{host}}/user/save
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

